<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Profecient</title>

	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bree+Serif&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.13.0/css/all.min.css">
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bree+Serif&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

	<style type="text/css">
		body{
			font-family: 'Bree Serif', serif;
		}
		.header{
			margin: 28px 55% 0 5%;
		}

		h1{
			margin-bottom: 0px;
			z-index: 2;
			position: relative;
			font-size: 5rem;
			color: white;
		}

		p{
			position: relative;
			z-index: 2;
			color: white;
			font-size: 1.5rem;
			padding-left: 10px;
		}

		.sign-up{
			position: absolute;
			z-index: 2;
			background: #3185FC;
			margin-top: 10px;
			border-radius: 25px;
			padding: 5px 15px;
			color: white;
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.login{
			position: absolute;
			z-index: 2;
			background: white;
			margin-top: 80px;
			border-radius: 20px;
			padding: 5px 15px;
			color: #3185FC;
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.sign-up:hover{
			color: white;
		}

		.login:hover{
			color: #3185FC;
		}


.slideshow{ 
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: 50% 50%;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  z-index: 0;
  background-image: url(https://images.pexels.com/photos/256520/pexels-photo-256520.jpeg) 
  /*animation: imageAnimation 50s linear infinite; */
}
	</style> 
</head>
<body>
	<div class="header">
		<div class="title">
			<h1><i class="fas fa-apple-alt"></i>  Profecient</h1>
			<p>A perfectly simple time management tool made for students.</p>
		</div>
		<div>
			<a class="sign-up" href="/signup">Sign Up for Free</a>
			<a class="login" href="/login">Login</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="slideshow">
		
	</div>
</body>
</html>

